interactivity.to_get_this_event: Autoplays after " Kittens " . This event belongs to an event chain started from " Rubik's Cube " .

progression.synopsis: Sensei gets asked to help test the best video game ever to be released. No affiliation with RAID: Shadow Legends . In order to beat the game, Sensei is tasked by Meowri, a familiar-looking cat girl, to gather the four elemental orbs and bring them to her house.
trivia: If Sensei meets the requirements, he can unlock a bonus area where he can face Fred, the game developer who acts as the game's super boss. If Sensei can beat him, he's rewarded with a memory of his past with Niki and Sekai .

changelog: This Event was added in Update 0.44.
